descriptionHtml:
[size=4][color=#ffd966][b][size=6]A Fabulous & Unnecessary mod by fredlaus: [color=#cc0000]#3[/color][/size][/b]
Why unnecessary mods?
Because they make your game beautiful.
You get more place to live, stack your stuff and house your followers
- and increase your self-esteem dramatically.[/color][color=#b6b6b6][size=4][color=#ffd966] He, he.[/color][/size]
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[/color][/size][color=#b6b6b6][size=4]I allways thought that the empty space besides The Red Wave on the Solitude Docks was annoying.
So here is another home for you, your stuff and your followers.
This ship would be familiar for those of you who use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74753/?]"Outlaws"[/url].
